metadata.name: HUMAN
metadata.description:
The fight for your individual freedoms and values is the last frontier. And every time you make a moral choice something gets born and something dies inside. 

"HUMAN" reflects on such choice by taking law enforcement officers as an example. They are powerful and authoritative figures by nature and most of them are dealing with moral dilemmas on a daily basis while on duty. 

To Serve and Protect.
To Serve and Protect.
